quickdt.predictiveModels.calibratedPredictiveModel

Class PAVCalibratedPredictiveModelBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • quickdt.predictiveModels.calibratedPredictiveModel.PAVCalibratedPredictiveModelBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PredictiveModelBuilder<CalibratedPredictiveModel>, UpdatablePredictiveModelBuilder<CalibratedPredictiveModel>

    public class PAVCalibratedPredictiveModelBuilder
extends Object
implements UpdatablePredictiveModelBuilder<CalibratedPredictiveModel>
    Created by alexanderhawk on 3/10/14. This class builds a calibrated predictive model, where the calibrator is implements the Pool Adjacent Violators algorithm. It currently has some severe implementation problems and it's use is not recommended.
